.com/uploads/wallpapers/2014/07/30/411138/67129eff711079cea6983a3636d5857a.jpg\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022color:rgb(221,221,221);text-decoration:none;\u0022 title=\u0022Maximize\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KERBAL SPACE PROGRAM sci-fi cartoon family ksp space flight simulator alien wallpaper background\u0022 height=\u0022417\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.wallpaperup.com/uploads/wallpapers/2014/07/30/411138/big_thumb_67129eff711079cea6983a3636d5857a.jpg\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u0022736\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/h5\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-16T16:39:43Z\u0022 title=\u002204/16/2016 04:39  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Matuchkin\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T16:54:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really like the second one in array 2, it matches so nicely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T17:18:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222517067\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137097\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460825663\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really like the second one in array 2, it matches so nicely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, that one is my favourite, I was actually considering putting it up as my wallpaper. We need more loading screens that look like this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fred Cop","CreatedById":146298,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T17:27:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUmm...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...in my mind, neither sets work. The first image of the first set does get repetitive, the third image is a copy of the second, and (also regarding the third image of the first set) it needs an update; the wings on that ship are the old Delta wings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...as for the second set, yes they are beautiful, but I think they are too enhanced. I don\u0027t want to see the images in the second set and think \u0027this is what KSP will look like!\u0027 only to play and be disappointed by the lack of scenery seen in the load-up images.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...but please bear in mind that this is what I think. I\u0027m a minority, and my opinion(s) have no impact unless they are carried by a large mob. Take what I think with a pinch of salt.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"guitarxe","CreatedById":115354,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T17:43:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the images, but after some time even they will get boring and repetitive. I think it would be nice if you could set up your own images to rotate during loading screens. For example a special folder in the game directory where you\u0027d drop in your screenshots and they would show up at random during the loading screen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketSquid","CreatedById":152665,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T17:52:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat would be really awesome is if:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nThere\u0027s a new folder titled \u0022LoadingScreens\u0022\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nEvery loading screen is randomly selected from the folder.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe pictures in the folder are 1280x720 PNG images, the same as screenshots.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nThis means that players can draw their own loading screens, use screenshots, or download new loading screens from the forums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gauga159","CreatedById":155603,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T18:25:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222517152\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137097\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460829125\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152665\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RocketSquid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n30 minutes ago, RocketSquid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat would be really awesome is if:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nThere\u0027s a new folder titled \u0022LoadingScreens\u0022\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nEvery loading screen is randomly selected from the folder.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe pictures in the folder are 1280x720 PNG images, the same as screenshots.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nThis means that players can draw their own loading screens, use screenshots, or download new loading screens from the forums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour idea looks promising but\u00A0shouldn\u0027t it have rotation rounds like 3 loading screens for one load then a second group of 3 loading screens\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tg626","CreatedById":112361,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T18:40:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do wish that like some other games, the loading screens were \u0022out in the open\u0022 where you could roll your own.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T18:46:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would like a plain black screen, so the game can spend that time loading the game instead of loading the loading screens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FullMetalMachinist","CreatedById":156531,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T19:49:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222517227\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137097\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460832372\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156657\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HebaruSan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, HebaruSan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would like a plain black screen, so the game can spend that time loading the game instead of loading the loading screens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would also like the developers to develop the game instead of making the loading screens customizable.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattinoz","CreatedById":118580,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T00:10:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStatus quo supporter here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe second set would be great for KSP prequel \u0022Kerbal Airways\u0022* but not so good for KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Assuming Kerbal Airways is something that exists outside of my head.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jlcarneiro","CreatedById":79196,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T00:28:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222517152\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137097\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460829125\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152665\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RocketSquid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 16/04/2016 at 2:52 PM, RocketSquid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat would be really awesome is if:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nThere\u0027s a new folder titled \u0022LoadingScreens\u0022\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nEvery loading screen is randomly selected from the folder.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe pictures in the folder are 1280x720 PNG images, the same as screenshots.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nThis means that players can draw their own loading screens, use screenshots, or download new loading screens from the forums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think the idea has the most chance of satisfying the most people: \u0022Don\u0027t like the loading screens? Use your own! If doesn\u0027t like the idea AT ALL, just leave the folder empty and a black loading screen will be shown...\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T00:37:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs that Scott Kerman picture a reference to Nassault\u0027s film \u0022Kerbal\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"max_creative","CreatedById":159640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-19T17:03:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTHE SECOND ONE IS SO AWESOME!!! 2nd FTW!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}